<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰飞走了，巴鲁自豪地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“毛克利记得老鹰的语言！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还找到了给我们发消息的办法！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看见了吧？”巴希拉说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我告诉过你，他非常聪明。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，我们最好马上去猴子城。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都知道猴子城在哪儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但几乎没有森林动物去过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是一个森林深处被废弃的老城。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有猴子喜欢使用人类用过的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“即使全速前进，也需要半个晚上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉边说边看着老熊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会尽量快点儿走的。”巴鲁保证道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不能等你。”巴希拉说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卡阿和我先走一步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你尽量跟上来吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没有脚。”卡阿说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我非常快。咱们走吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁急急忙忙跟在卡阿和巴希拉的后面，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但很快，他就停下来气喘吁吁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉一直跑着，卡阿好像把身体贴在地上一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蟒蛇找到了穿过森林的捷径，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他目光坚定，沿路前行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利仔细看着猴子城。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这里已经成了一片废墟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，很久以前一个国王建起了这座城。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大理石墙的内外长着树，野生藤蔓挂在窗户框上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山顶上有一座没有屋顶的宫殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>宫殿下面是一排排房子和空坑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地上是寺庙破碎的圆顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们叫这个地方 “猴子城”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他们不知道怎么使用人类建筑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们坐在大理石房间里抓跳蚤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们沿着露台跑来跑去，摇晃橙子树，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只为了看水果掉下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在蓄水池里喝水、打架。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每隔一段时间，猴子们会厌倦这座城市。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们就会回到树梢上去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天，猴子们很晚才到了猴子城。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然走了很远的路，但他们没去睡觉，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而是手拉手跳起了舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只猴子还讲了一段很长的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个人类孩子将改变猴子的历史！”他宣布，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个男孩儿将告诉我们怎么把树枝编在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们能盖房子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利叹了一口气，开始把一些树枝编到一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几只猴子试图模仿他做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可他们一只接一只地觉得无聊，站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一些猴子开始拉朋友们的尾巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一些唱着歌跳来跳去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于， 毛克利放弃了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他放下树枝。“我饿了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>二十只猴子跳起来要去给毛克利拿坚果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在路上就打了起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把食物的事情忘得一干二净。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“巴鲁是对的。”毛克利想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猴子们没有规则，也没有头领。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们只知道偷东西和唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要回家！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利站起来向大门走去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但猴子们一下子就拽住了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！不行！你得跟我们在一起！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么想走？”一只猴子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们是森林里最棒的动物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们会告诉你我们有多棒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的猴子都聚到露台听那个愚蠢的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利忍不住笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很好奇他们睡不睡觉。”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抬头看，发现一朵云彩正在滑向月亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，天就会完全黑下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到时候，他将再次尝试逃跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>